data.description: Introducing a spacious and inviting home in the heart of a thriving retirement community! This charming residence offers over 1700 square feet of comfortable living space, providing the perfect backdrop for your golden years.    Features:     • Bedrooms: With three generously sized bedrooms, there’s room for guests, hobbies, and relaxation.   • Bathrooms: Two well-appointed bathrooms ensure your comfort and convenience.   • High Ceilings: The high ceilings throughout the home create an open and airy atmosphere, adding to the sense of spaciousness.   • Garage: A two-car garage not only protects your vehicles but also provides valuable storage space.   • In-Ground Pool: Dive into the delight of your very own in-ground pool, completely screened in to keep the bugs at bay and extend your poolside enjoyment.   • Community Amenities: Enjoy the numerous amenities the community offers, including a pool, workout center, and convenient shopping options right at your doorstep.   • Golf Cart Friendly: Embrace the golf cart lifestyle, exploring the neighborhood and running errands with ease.    This home is more than just a house; it’s a gateway to a vibrant retirement lifestyle. Don’t miss the opportunity to make it yours and start enjoying the best years of your life in style and comfort.
